{"tid":1978982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［發夢］警犬戰術性後退問題","createTime":"2020-04-19T06:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T16:30:39.000Z","uid":249703,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6009e7a8f3527eb48e3fc4195c7db8687b992d","tid":1978982,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"疫情開始收皮，支那開始明刀明槍收窄自由<br />\n黎緊既重要日子（eg 7.1）大家有可能會再「合法上街」<br />\n以下問題應該點拆？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n612 當日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190613&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20702787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190613%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20702787&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=97e0a2c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190613%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20702787&h=ca053f9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20190613&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20702787</a><br />\n<br />\n不過，警方其後在添華道兩端的防線都有異動，調走前線配備盾牌的警員，分別後退入特首辦及立法會範圍。示威者見防線轉弱，於是同步衝擊並趁機清走防線前的鐵馬陣。<br />\n<br />\n而在立法會停車場外，另一批示威者衝向把守立法會外牆的10多名警員，由於人數差距太大，警員敗退至停車場入口；兩批示威者匯集後成功突破封鎖線，衝入立法會示威區，進一步逼近立法會大門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理大圍城當日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191202&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60325128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191202%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60325128&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=bd10a41b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191202%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60325128&h=02434078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191202&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60325128</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生還者Ocean當時從果欄一帶前進至窩打老道與彌敦道交界，彌敦道一邊是示威者，窩打老道是警察防線，起初窩打老道警察防線一直後退，讓示威者推前，「橫街卻忽然衝出警察，前後包抄彌敦道示威者。」Ocean認為警方是策略性退後，引示威者推進，再一次過兩邊夾擊，促成突如其來的逃亡潮，「結果窩打老道的示威者跟彌敦道的示威者同一時間，幾百人衝去碧街，那狹窄路口是唯一能走的路線。我自己走時也踩到手足。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n差唔多六月，不論你係和理非定前線請準備好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973875</a>"},{"pid":"05681c75889f3c3093c407136c52c2f63a1b30e0","tid":1978982,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f6e9e3bd4408049e9fdb9c6d300c31e32db408b","tid":1978982,"uid":7179,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"做好哨 唔好盲推<br />\n或者<br />\n一推推到底 見到狗衝照衝話去"},{"pid":"19d6199f2018233756adf5b4427ebc8bef37062e","tid":1978982,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1f9e4f19329eb17cbd4bd75c87940cb755b2c2","tid":1978982,"uid":309001,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:27:44.000Z","msg":"又出去送頭？"},{"pid":"d05df37bbde6d0f3b45f7eb4fd623d25ae34828f","tid":1978982,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"請君入甕"},{"pid":"e299d68b6c3f4dfffc69a3beba1d4d9ef463e125","tid":1978982,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"推係為左多啲正經post入返大家眼球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c082f3918cb808095d8d197deb33b70e6af1c2","tid":1978982,"uid":76745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"答案喺第82空降師"},{"pid":"1db05d63b238d51c330bd678bdd5f77c59e4a44f","tid":1978982,"uid":30966,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:35:24.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - plankton )"},{"pid":"0fec38bd2746589953e3727ec964d9293a4c5cca","tid":1978982,"uid":315329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT